Summary: Photo of unknown object releasing chemtrails
divs: Sighting DetailsI was observing what appeared to be a jet at high altitude, approx 30-35,000 ft. with a very clear and noticable trail being emitted. I wasnt able to see the plane so I zoomed in as best I could and was able to get this one picture. After examineing it I decided to submit it to your organization. I was taking a break from mowing when I noticed it. I have other photos a few hours later of the sky that evening. Probably moot but it did rain for several hours on sunday may 30th.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Monroe
